title: Week 5 NFL Recap, Analysis; Colts hand Chiefs their first loss (Football 10/7)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough to recap and analyze all 13 games from Sunday's Week 5 slate. The guys discuss: Colts-Chiefs (4:00), Bears-Raiders (16:00), Packers-Cowboys (23:00), Pats-Redskins (32:30), Jags-Panthers (40:00), Bucs-Saints (48:00), Falcons-Texans (55:00), Ravens-Steelers (1:01:00), Cardinals-Bengals, Jets-Eagles, Giants-Vikings, Bills-Titans and Broncos-Chargers.
